replies.body:
I see... I do agree that there are quite a few people that argue like that and it generally makes me laugh, so I do understand where your point is coming from.

Some of the points you showed there are kind of humorous though :)

{{sticker:slayer-jinx-wink}} 

Sadly that is what humans are like. They generally want to defend the things they enjoy. I do that too, I can't deny it.

Thank you for being kind and patient. I'm sure I may have made a mistake or two in my arguments but I'm glad you aren't rude about it.

{{sticker:katarina-love}}
